</a>
<div class='talk-speaker__details media__message'>
<div class='talk-speaker__name h10'>
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mathias_jud">Mathias Jud</a>
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__description'>
Artist
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__bio'>
The work of artists Mathias Jud and Christoph Wachter questions the limits of our communication possibilities and, therefore, of our identity.
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/mathias_jud">Full bio</a>
</div>
